Tepco Says It Lost Control of Pressure at Fukushima Reactors

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u   a n d   M i c h i o   N a k a y a m a
-- 
2011-03-11T22:52:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/tepco-says-it-lost-control-of-pressure-at-fukushima-reactors.html
Tokyo Electric Power Co. said it
has lost control of pressure building up at three reactors of
its nuclear power plant in earthquake-struck Fukushima
prefecture north of Tokyo.  Temperatures in the control room at the plant have risen
higher than 100 Celsius (212 Fahrenheit), said Naoki Tsunoda, 
a company spokesman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jim McDonald at 
 jmcdonald8@bloomberg.net  